Dancer-Plugin-ValidateTiny version 0.01
=======================================

Dancer::Plugin::ValidateTiny - Validate::Tiny dancer plugin.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Dancer
  Dancer::Plugin
  Validate::Tiny
  Email::Valid

